    "body": "The `stateMutability` field was introduced with 0.4.16 (**2017-08-14**), which deprecated both the `constant` and `payable` fields. `stateMutability: 'view'` (what you have above) has the same effect as \"constant\" had previously.\r\n\r\nThis was announced multiple times. Apparently more than 2 years was not enough for tools to catch up :wink:",
